          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1614613091906-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion petals are softening, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1614613109531-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
