            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>halloumi</strong></p><p>Transfer the<strong> smoky tomato beans</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated halloumi </strong>then sprinkle the<strong> dried oregano </strong>over the top</p><p>Put the dish under the grill for 5 min or until the halloumi has begun to melt and crisp up – these are your <strong>halloumi-topped smoky</strong> <strong>tomato beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
