    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the dish is under the grill, wash the<strong> gem</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and pat dry, then cut into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
